  "summary": "Little Simz brought her unique flair to the kitchen, cooking up one of her favourite comfort foods: rasta pasta. The bold flavours of jerk spices and scotch bonnet blend perfectly with a creamy, rich cheese sauce, creating a dish that's fiery, indulgent, and really tasty. With a vibrant mix of colourful vegetables and tender pasta, this rasta pasta is the perfect balance of heat and creaminess. Whether you're looking for something to spice up your weeknight dinner or impress guests, Little Simz's take on rasta pasta is an absolute winner for any occasion.",
